{"tid":1853361,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"手足之後唔好再向狗屋擲汽油彈","createTime":"2020-01-31T02:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T17:40:26.000Z","uid":2719,"like":26,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0b10aa2191d04c44276e94dcf71d3716ea3654","tid":1853361,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/icfhRW1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FicfhRW1.jpg&h=0bc1e59d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【1.29抗疫黎明】#天水圍 0753<br />\n<br />\n據消息指今天稍早時分，天水圍警署遭投擲汽油彈，警署外牆及水馬被燻黑。<br />\n<br />\n#理大校園電台 @hkpusucampusradio<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n一張banner都可以派10幾隻狗去守幾日，依家你挑釁完班狗，佢地揾狗24小時輪班mon cctv𥄫實狗署門口唔係無可能。<br />\n<br />\n我明白擲狗屋唔係死物咁簡單，係有象徵可以挑戰政權嘅意義，其實大家都收到，係時候停止，太危險。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係叫大家做休息撚，只係與其再做大家已收到你訊息嘅事，不如做其他，做乜無所謂，擲狗都無所謂，但就唔好再係人地主場搞事，至少隔一段長時間等狗鬆懈先。<br />\n<br />\n最後，黑警死全家，大家染病記得去狗屋。"},{"pid":"ff06ea5fff3ca266f626b37745df8313821ecafb","tid":1853361,"uid":122275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:37:00.000Z","msg":"成間燒撚左佢就大劑<div style=\"text-align: left;\"></div>"},{"pid":"052b01760ac21bf7a068a4592e02e58c450597c2","tid":1853361,"uid":17232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"x"},{"pid":"d47b4724a3df93c67ebe58c0f23e7715096618ce","tid":1853361,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"次次都冇狗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"587ae35a9a1d6921508da73ba24939251a09e83d","tid":1853361,"uid":307270,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-31T02:47:18.000Z","msg":"掟用過嘅口罩<br />\n最多罰1500"},{"pid":"2571f24769456442347d4a6c1e4f082656ce12b2","tid":1853361,"uid":187232,"like":8,"dislike":1,"scor